metadata.name: Holiday Armadillos
metadata.description:
This year was very eventful for all those connected via NFT community. We saw the Merge, still surviving the bear market and carry our hopes for a better 2023.  
Holiday Armadillos is a fun illustration of memorable journey in web3 this year.  
This is my first edition drop. Hope this art bring a smile on your face and warm your heart as it did to me when I got connected with you in web3.
